orbit-status (1.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Hyprland IPC: real-time workspace/window events via event socket.
  * Track windows per workspace, display pretty workspace names.
  * Show active window title in bar (configurable via show_active_window).
  * Inotify-based event-driven Lua plugin updates for battery/brightness/network.
  * Workspace switching uses Hyprland command socket directly.

 -- steven66619 <ste@example.com>  Tue, 19 May 2026 22:00:00 +0000

