  * Add bundled Lua plugin for weather.

 -- steven66619 <ste@example.com>  Sun, 17 May 2026 22:40:00 +0000

orbit-status (1.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Lua plugin architecture — all system modules are now Lua scripts.
  * New config keys: lua_plugin_N_path, show_lua_plugin_N, lua_plugin_N_prefix,
    lua_plugin_N_color, click_lua_plugin_N.
  * Bundled Lua plugins for CPU, memory, disk, volume, network, battery, updates.
  * Lua API: tick(), on_click(), on_tooltip(), interval variable.
  * Removed hardcoded C modules (show_cpu, show_mem, etc.) and custom command
    modules — replaced by generic Lua plugin system.

 -- steven66619 <ste@example.com>  Sun, 17 May 2026 22:10:00 +0000

